      problem: 'With   10,000+ employees   using internal platforms, support teams handled   500+ tickets daily  , with most being repetitive queries about workflows, policies, and basic troubleshooting.   Average response time: 4–6 hours  . Complex issues took days. Users were frustrated by delays, and support teams were overwhelmed handling the same questions repeatedly. There was no unified, self-service support system.',
