        'Drove Slack integration decision by demonstrating 4x higher engagement in Slack prototypes vs web-only version, convincing stakeholders to deprioritize web app',
        'Championed admin dashboard and monitoring tools to give Support team ownership of content and performance, building long-term sustainability'
      ],
      beforeAfter: [
        '**Before:** 500+ daily support tickets, 4–6 hour average response time, 70% of tickets were repetitive questions, support team overwhelmed',
        '**After:** 65% query reduction through automation, <1 hour response time, support team focused on complex issues, 24/7 availability, 88% employee satisfaction'
      ],
      finalSolution: 'The LLM-Powered Conversational Support Platform provides instant, chat-based support through web and Slack interfaces. The system follows a simple flow:   User query → LLM understanding → Response → Escalation   (if needed). Employees ask questions in natural language, and the system provides guided, task-based responses. For complex queries, the platform escalates to human support with full context. The interface is optimized for non-technical users and includes feedback mechanisms to improve accuracy.',
      impact: [
        'Reduced support queries by   65%   through automated responses',
        'Improved response time by   75%   (from 4–6 hours to under 1 hour)',
        'Cut support costs by   45%   by automating routine inquiries',
        'Handled   15,000+ conversations   in first 3 months',
