        'Increased employee satisfaction with support from   62% → 88%  ',
        'Freed support team capacity to focus on complex issues',
        'Enabled 24/7 support availability for global workforce'
      ],
      learnings: [
        'Guided responses work better than open-ended AI for specific use cases',
        'LLM should understand intent, not be the source of truth',
        'Escalation to humans builds trust and handles edge cases gracefully',
        'Conversational UI must feel helpful and approachable, not robotic',
        'Feedback loops improve accuracy and user confidence over time',
        'Integration with existing tools (Slack) drives immediate adoption'
      ]
